<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Availability Override Created</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
        .override {
            background-color: #e2e3e5;
            border: 1px solid #d6d8db;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .note {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeeba;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Special Availability Override</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>A special availability override has been created for your schedule.</p>
        
        <div class="override">
            <h3>Override Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
            <p><strong>Original Hours:</strong> {{originalHours}}</p>
            <p><strong>Override Hours:</strong> {{overrideHours}}</p>
            {{#if reason}}
            <p><strong>Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
            {{/if}}
        </div>
        
        <div class="note">
            <p>This override will temporarily replace your regular availability for the specified date.</p>
            <p>Your regular schedule will resume automatically after this date.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>You can review or modify this override through your provider dashboard.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        <p>&copy; 2025 Eventide. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
